                  "D-BE"
                ],
                "reaction": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " Deuteron energy was 23.2 MeV."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "INC-SPECT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The mean neutron energy for 0.3 - 23 MeV, at a deuteron",
                "bombarding energy of 23.2 MeV, is 7.5 MeV",
                " (From M.A.Lone et al, Nucl.Instr.Meth.,143(1977)331).",
                "The neutron spectrum, as determined previously from an",
                "spectrum unfolding measurement, was verified using the",
                "measured activities of the Al-27(n,a)Na-24,",
                "Au-197(n,2n)Au-196 and Nb-93(n,2n)Nb-92m reactions."
              ]
            }
          ],
